{"tid":2375342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾祈殷：預計要到2022年年底，港人才可重新出外旅遊","createTime":"2021-01-22T03:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T05:18:54.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8ca05acb93eb3e0cbcedd83e814c904fa3f9e5bc","tid":2375342,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:17:54.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情肆虐一年，由最初口罩供應緊絀，到分析疫情發展、防疫措施和疫苗等，都不乏民間專家頻頻講解，其中感染及傳染病專科醫生曾祈殷於03年沙士時開始接受專科訓練，未料17年後再次遇上大疫症，雖然已離開公院，但一直緊貼事態分析疫情。他直言自己也有「抗疫疲勞」，更預計要到2022年底，全球疫情才會真正受控，愛旅遊的港人才可重新出行...<br />\n<br />\n對於疫苗即將到來，他預計本港要達到人口7成人都接種疫苗，才能產生群體免疫，但抗體能否維持一年、是否要補打仍是未知之數，亦可能出現「售後副作用」，各國人民接種疫苗後出現不良反應。他估計要到2022年年末，各國才可能打完疫苗，全球疫情受控，屆時港人終可安心旅遊...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/PASKOKUPNVBM5G3C4MMQPAJZMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122%2FPASKOKUPNVBM5G3C4MMQPAJZMQ%2F&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=14aac152\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210122%2FPASKOKUPNVBM5G3C4MMQPAJZMQ%2F&h=19382420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210122/PASKOKUPNVBM5G3C4MMQPAJZMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"2895f3df88cf3560865530dae1aea85437ba8746","tid":2375342,"uid":241239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15399561c36633ab856b1b616769c50477ce261e","tid":2375342,"uid":93600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5b41952e9dea8f612a5a5a6513cfad36169e76","tid":2375342,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos